snippet.title: Arena of Evolution: Red Tides
snippet.description:
Arena of Evolution: Red Tides is a global-server auto-chess game. You can select pieces from 9 classes and 13 races to form a lineup and upgrade their levels, use racial and class bonds and different pieces ultimate skills, and battle it out with seven other players in the same arena for victory!

Subscribe for more! ►►https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCl-d-lgaX28_y-vbGEEDkAQ
